        <updateDate>2024-07-03T17:16:05Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stop Tax Penalties on American Hostages Act of 2024&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill postpones certain tax filing deadlines for U.S. nationals and their spouses who are unlawfully or wrongfully detained abroad or held hostage abroad. It also allows for a refund and abatement of penalties and fines paid by detained individuals.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
